00:13:43,640 --> 00:13:45,370
saya berpeluang untuk menang.

232
00:13:45,420 --> 00:13:47,950
Adik, awak tak berani ke?

233
00:13:51,070 --> 00:13:51,910
Bergurau.

234
00:13:52,850 --> 00:13:53,600
Marilah.

235
00:14:01,150 --> 00:14:02,110
Taruh semua?

236
00:14:02,700 --> 00:14:03,530
Berani.

237
00:14:05,160 --> 00:14:06,450
Saya suka.

238
00:14:09,960 --> 00:14:10,900
Mulalah.

239
00:14:12,610 --> 00:14:13,360
Jadi...

240
00:14:13,990 --> 00:14:15,070
Saya akan bermula.

241
00:14:28,490 --> 00:14:29,320
Cepatnya.

242
00:14:37,990 --> 00:14:38,660
Di sini.

243
00:14:39,280 --> 00:14:40,110
Sila pilih.

244
00:14:41,530 --> 00:14:44,280
Takkan salah, yang paling kiri.

245
00:14:45,070 --> 00:14:46,379
Pilih yang paling kiri itu.

246
00:14:46,380 --> 00:14:49,240
Jadi, encik ini nak taruh cawan yang mana?

247
00:14:50,350 --> 00:14:51,750
Saya tak nak taruh cawan.

248
00:14:51,900 --> 00:14:53,559
Saya nak taruh pada tangan kanan awak.

249
00:14:53,560 --> 00:14:55,690
Awak tahu main tak? Jangan buat kacau.

250
00:14:57,610 --> 00:15:00,200
Apa yang dia mahu buat sebenarnya?

251
00:15:01,530 --> 00:15:03,390
Encik maksudkan tangan saya ini?

252
00:15:03,570 --> 00:15:05,159
Tergamak dia tiba-tiba tukar tangan.

253
00:15:05,160 --> 00:15:06,490
Tangannya cukup cepat.

254
00:15:06,840 --> 00:15:09,500
Tak, saya tukar bertaruh pada tangan kiri awak.

255
00:15:09,690 --> 00:15:10,620
Untuk keadilan,

256
00:15:10,640 --> 00:15:13,969
sila letakkan kedua-dua tangan awak di atas meja dan jangan bergerak.

257
00:15:13,970 --> 00:15:16,160
Cepat buka, jangan main helah.

258
00:15:22,240 --> 00:15:25,029
Tahniah kepada encik kerana memenangi cip berganda!

259
00:15:25,030 --> 00:15:25,780
Mustahil.

260
00:15:27,060 --> 00:15:28,390
Boleh main seperti ini?

261
00:15:30,550 --> 00:15:32,880
Memang tiada syiling di bawah tiga cawan.

262
00:15:33,810 --> 00:15:35,060
Masalahnya di mana?

263
00:15:35,720 --> 00:15:37,070
Maaf, encik.

264
00:15:37,920 --> 00:15:40,989
Tapi peraturan tak menunjukkan bahawa ini melanggar peraturan.

265
00:15:40,990 --> 00:15:43,530
Adakah pada masa itu?

266
00:15:44,800 --> 00:15:46,930
Sebenarnya dia sediakan dua syiling.

267
00:15:47,700 --> 00:15:49,489
Satu tersembunyi di tapak tangan,

268
00:15:49,490 --> 00:15:51,450
satu dibuang ke bawah meja

269
00:15:51,530 --> 00:15:53,489
semasa berhenti memusingkan cawan.

270
00:15:53,490 --> 00:15:54,450
Perangkap.

271
00:15:55,500 --> 00:15:57,779
Soalan mengenai bagaimana syiling berada pada tangan

272
00:15:57,780 --> 00:15:58,990
tak boleh dijawab.

273
00:16:03,240 --> 00:16:05,240
Tiada apa-apa perangkap, encik.

274
00:16:05,820 --> 00:16:08,249
Dari awal hingga akhir, hanya ada satu syiling.

275
00:16:08,250 --> 00:16:09,180
Awak yang kalah,

276
00:16:09,730 --> 00:16:10,330
encik.

277
00:16:11,780 --> 00:16:12,410
Tak guna.

278
00:16:13,490 --> 00:16:15,320
Saya pun tak dapat teka.

279
00:16:17,520 --> 00:16:18,470
Orang ini...

280
00:16:19,630 --> 00:16:20,550
Orang ini...

281
00:16:21,910 --> 00:16:23,450
Siapa dia sebenarnya?

282
00:16:26,910 --> 00:16:27,460
Lima.

283
00:16:31,660 --> 00:16:32,280
Mulalah.

284
00:16:34,610 --> 00:16:35,740
Saya tergesa-gesa.

285
00:16:42,360 --> 00:16:45,699
Pendek kata, beberapa ujian dah berlalu dengan macam-macam aktiviti.

286
00:16:45,700 --> 00:16:48,100
Akhirnya dapat kumpulkan bilangan orang.

287
00:16:57,780 --> 00:16:59,910
Mengalu-alukan calon yang terakhir.

288
00:17:00,160 --> 00:17:01,450
Maka misi kami

289
00:17:01,910 --> 00:17:03,310
untuk kamu akan bermula.

290
00:17:12,530 --> 00:17:14,760
Tahniah kepada semua yang lulus pelbagai pemilihan.

291
00:17:12,589 --> 00:17:16,530
{\an8}[Pratonton episod seterusnya]

292
00:17:15,000 --> 00:17:16,879
Mari kita mempersilakan Tuan Piao.

293
00:17:16,880 --> 00:17:20,079
Semua ini ganjaran untuk pemberani.

294
00:17:20,829 --> 00:17:22,630
Gerakan buaya itu memang cepat,

295
00:17:23,170 --> 00:17:24,979
tapi kawasan serangannya terhad.

296
00:17:24,980 --> 00:17:26,040
Takkan jumpa lagi!

297
00:17:27,750 --> 00:17:29,830
Di mana wira yang seterusnya?

298
00:17:31,080 --> 00:17:32,480
Yan Luo, awak tunggulah.

299
00:17:33,210 --> 00:17:34,599
Saya mesti dapat cari awak.

300
00:17:34,600 --> 00:17:37,330
Mari kita melangkau permulaan yang membosankan

301
00:17:37,500 --> 00:17:38,840
dan mulakan aktiviti.

302
00:17:39,750 --> 00:17:42,130
Saya harap semua dapat berseronok.

303
00:17:46,150 --> 00:17:47,400
♪ Seperti satu mimpi ♪

304
00:17:49,310 --> 00:17:52,310
♪ Ingin sentuhmu tapi terjatuh ♪

305
00:17:52,480 --> 00:17:54,100
♪ Dalam lautan manusia ♪

306
00:17:55,610 --> 00:17:59,200
♪ Seperti ditolak ke dalam pusaran yang tiada batasan ♪

307
00:17:59,230 --> 00:18:04,140
♪ Aku yang berada di luar sinaranmu ♪

308
00:18:04,190 --> 00:18:07,640
♪ Bagaimana mendekatimu dan menyampaikan ♪

309
00:18:07,730 --> 00:18:13,350
♪ Suara rindu itu ♪

310
00:18:13,440 --> 00:18:16,350
♪ Dah tak sempat ♪

311
00:18:16,390 --> 00:18:24,519
♪ Cerita sampai ke sini, hanya tinggal aku seorang ♪

312
00:18:24,520 --> 00:18:25,850
♪ Kelopak bunga yang berterbang ♪

313
00:18:27,560 --> 00:18:31,190
♪ Bagaikan kekesalan yang tak dipenuhi ♪

314
00:18:36,940 --> 00:18:40,230
♪ Sebelum langit berbintang gelap ♪

315
00:18:40,690 --> 00:18:44,900
♪ Bolehkah aku melihatmu sekali lagi?♪

316
00:18:45,640 --> 00:18:49,810
♪ Walaupun kau takkan perasan ♪

317
00:18:49,980 --> 00:18:53,230
♪ Kenangan terdampar di dada ♪

318
00:18:53,480 --> 00:18:56,480
♪ Tiba-tiba jatuh ke dalam jurang ♪

319
00:18:56,690 --> 00:18:58,270
♪ Aku pejamkan mata ♪

320
00:18:58,440 --> 00:19:02,020
♪ Tak sanggup melihat masa silam muncul semula ♪

321
00:19:02,810 --> 00:19:05,980
♪ Ucapkan selamat tinggal ♪

322
00:19:06,020 --> 00:19:08,390
♪ Masih bermundar-mandir ♪

323
00:19:09,140 --> 00:19:12,020
♪ Macam mana aku boleh?♪

324
00:19:12,270 --> 00:19:15,190
♪ Lepaskan tangan dan rasa lega ♪

325
00:19:15,540 --> 00:19:18,490
♪ Ucapkan selamat tinggal ♪

326
00:19:18,520 --> 00:19:21,830
♪ Pergi tanpa memiliki apa-apa ♪

327
00:19:22,140 --> 00:19:24,930
♪ Di manakah cahayaku?♪

328
00:19:25,110 --> 00:19:28,240
♪ Tinggal saja kekosongan di depan mata ♪

